  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0d82\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dab\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0dba\u0dd1\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A decline in tourist arrivals",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Compared to the month of July, the arrival of tourists to the country in August shows a significant decrease.",
        "In July, 47,293 tourists came to Sri Lanka and in August, the number dropped by 20 percent to 37,760.",
        "496 420 tourists have come to Sri Lanka till the end of August this year. A target of one million tourists is expected for Sri Lanka this year and to complete it, 5 lakh tourists should be brought to Sri Lanka in another four months.",
        "In August, the largest number of tourists came to Sri Lanka from England, India and Germany respectively."
      ],
